{"tid":2253167,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林子博不捨太太離世流下男兒淚 子女留言給媽媽︰我哋會照顧好自己","createTime":"2020-10-22T03:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T07:39:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89888269a8f9e195a1cfc95cdf048e3cffbeeb7c","tid":2253167,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"前大台娛樂主播林子博的太太董燕君（Shirley），去年確診患上罕見癌症「平滑肌肉瘤（腹腔）」第4期，可惜近月病情反覆，昨晨不敵癌魔病逝。昨日子博在社交網透露太太離世的消息後，一整天都忙於太太的身後事。到今日凌晨時份他在社交網發文抒發情感，並流下男兒淚，他寫道︰「看着你離開時，我沒有太多的淚水，還以為自己已有充足的心理準備，但當靜下時才發現，原來我還未Ready，到底怎樣才可以令眼淚停下來。」可見他對愛妻的離開，十分不捨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/TD65XE6JMZALXLG6DBLQK3CGVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FTD65XE6JMZALXLG6DBLQK3CGVA%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=1cd1245a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FTD65XE6JMZALXLG6DBLQK3CGVA%2F&h=369fd5c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/TD65XE6JMZALXLG6DBLQK3CGVA/</a>"},{"pid":"1637cb85ea3192e1fb98d99d7d6f50efc52465c9","tid":2253167,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1b411a142b748a28050769a0f5eb250f5c50b1","tid":2253167,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實點解一驗會去到第四期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係無明顯症狀？"},{"pid":"7d359cae5f2e74255146815e3acfa9844e32250a","tid":2253167,"uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e1b411a142b748a28050769a0f5eb250f5c50b1","tid":2253167,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實點解一驗會去到第四期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係唔係無明顯症狀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-2